                               "In proceedings"]]
                 [agenda-tag "April 1, 2019"])
     :content [:p "“Implementing Baker’s " [:code "SUBTYPEP"] " Decision Procedure”, based on my research
work at LRDE. Presentation of an alternative implementation for " [:code "SUBTYPEP"] ", a standard
